Tue Sep 18 21:19:46 2001  John Ellis  <johne@bellatlantic.net>

	* collect.c, filelist.[ch], globals.c, gqview.h, main.c, menu.c,
	rcfile.c, typedefs.h, window.c: Added sort files ascending/descending
