	* dnd.c, filelist.c, gqview.h, menu.c: Dragging and right clicking on
	file list no longer displays image, but correctly, only displays
	action/popup menu.
	* globals.c, gqview.h, img-main.c, main.c, menu.c, window.c: Add full
	screen option.

